sub_title: A multi-disciplinary Marketing professional and a well-seasoned Pop Culture specialist
summary:
As an international marketing strategist, I work best in a versatile and challenging environment. My knowledge fields are technology, entertainment and lifestyle, due to my experience and affiliation with these branches. I work well both on national and international level, and have a high affinity and work experience in both Europe and Asia (namely South-Korea and India)

Specialties: Creative strategies, communication, (online) marketing, intercultural business and awareness, innovative thinking, online media intelligence and etiquette, and concept development.
